OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FA parish councillor assaulted by a
OL,7,Fbusinessman in a planning row has told
OL,8,FITV News: "Disputes are usually
OL,9,Fsettled with a bottle of wine not
OL,10,Fviolence".
OL,12,FAndrew Mason, the chairman of Church
OL,13,FFenton Parish Council, was attacked as
OL,14,Fhe lay in front of a cherry picker in
OL,15,Fan attempt to protect nesting birds in
OL,16,Fthe village of Church Fenton, North
OL,17,FYorkshire.
