OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FMr Mason said: "To say I was in a
OL,7,Fstate of shock was an understatement.
OL,8,FI thought, oh my god, who behaves like
OL,9,Fthat? (I was) literally in a state of
OL,10,Fshock.
OL,12,F"I thought how could that happen? How
OL,13,Fwould somebody do something like that?
OL,15,F"The last time I was in a fight... I
OL,16,Fwas six."
