OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FThe incident happened after Chris
OL,7,FMakin, the boss of Leeds East Airport,
OL,8,Fsuccessfully applied for permission
OL,9,Ffor trees to be cut back to make way
OL,10,Ffor aircraft.
OL,12,FMr Mason, 63, objected to the move,
OL,13,Farguing birds nesting in the trees
OL,14,Fshould not be disturbed.
OL,16,FHe was walking to work at Church
OL,17,FFenton community shop on 4 April 2023
OL,18,Fwhen a cherry picker moved in to begin
OL,19,Fthe work.
