OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FHe said: "Contrary to what people say
OL,7,FI'm not brave, let's get that
OL,8,Fstraight. So I walked underneath the
OL,9,Fcherry picker."
OL,11,FIn scenes caught on camera, Mr Mason
OL,12,Fcan be seen in front of the cherry
OL,13,Fpicker as Makin, 65, tries to drag him
OL,14,Fout of the way by his clothes and hair.
OL,16,FMichael Smith, prosecuting, told
OL,17,FHarrogate Magistrates Court: "The
OL,18,Fdefendant scooped Mr Mason's hair into
OL,19,Fhis hands and tried to pull him across
OL,20,Fthe road by his hair."
