OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FIn the video, Mr Mason is seen lying
OL,7,Fon the floor and can be heard shouting
OL,8,F"get off me" and "the police are on
OL,9,Ftheir way, you lunatic" as well as
OL,10,Fcalling Making an "ignorant bully" as
OL,11,Fthe defendant swears at him.
OL,13,FIn a victim statement read to the
OL,14,Fcourt, Mr Mason said that, at that
OL,15,Fpoint, he thought "my life is in
OL,16,Fperil".
OL,18,FHe expressed dismay that he "could be
OL,19,Fviciously attacked in broad daylight
OL,20,Fin the village I love and where I have
OL,21,Fbrought up my children".
