OL,3,C'Disbelief' of parish councillor
OL,4,Cassaulted in row over trees
OL,6,FMr Mason, who has been a councillor
OL,7,Ffor 14 years, said it has not put him
OL,8,Foff standing up for what he believes
OL,9,Fis right.
OL,11,FHe said: "We get involved in all sorts
OL,12,Fbut it's what you call neighbours
OL,13,Fdisputes - but we live in a lovely
OL,14,Flittle village, it's normally resolved
OL,15,Fwith a bottle of wine - not the level
OL,16,Fof violence I was subjected to last
OL,17,Fyear."
